g_id=1&keyword=&category=&author=10&month=&search.x=22&search.y=13&search=Go Posts at Worldchanging.com]\n* [http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Issue/story?oid=oid:597178 \"In Your Facebook\"]\n* [http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Issue/story?oid=oid:613622 \"The Serious Play in Saving the World\"]\n\n==References==\n*{{cite web |url= http://www.austinchronicle.com/issues/vol15/issue48/screens.lebkowsky.html |title=Cyberculture Evolution |first1=Jon |last1=Lebkowsky |first2=R.U. |last2=Sirius |authorlink2=R. U. Sirius |editor=Jen Scoville |work=austinchronicle.com |date=August 1996 |accessdate=12 December 2013}}\n*{{cite web |url= http://technoccult.net/archives/2010/05/27/participatory-medicine-with-jon-lebkowsky-technoccult-interview/ |title=Participatory medicine with Jon Lebkowsky |first=Klint |last=Finley |work=technoccult.net |date=27 May 2010 |accessdate=12 December 2013}}\n*{{cite web |url= http://www.briancombs.net/3350/ |title=Austin's Internet Pioneers - Jon Lebkowsky |first=Brian |last=Combs |work=briancombs.net |date=16 December 2009 |accessdate=12 December 2013}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Jon Lebkowsky}}\n* [http://weblogsky.com Weblogsky Blog]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070226185834/http://www.polycot.com/team/jon/ Polycot Team Listing]\n* [http://effaustin.org EFF-Austin]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20061205053124/http://wirelessfuture.org/ Wireless Future]\n* [http://dcitexas.org Digital Convergence Initiative]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070219091606/http://www.worldchanging.com/bios/jonl.html Worldchanging Bio]\n* [http://www.itconversations.com/shows/detail1076.html Political Networks (ITConversations)]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060429210542/http://www.authorviews.com/authors/lebkowsky/video.php AuthorViews video interview about Extreme Democracy]\n* [http://www.austinchronicle.com/issues/vol15/issue48/screens.lebkowsky.html From Zines to Zen: RU Sirius interviews Jon Lebkowsky] 1996\n* [https:/